1. *Čujemo* da je njegov glas sve jači (We hear that his voice is getting louder). 
2. Neki *čuju* njegov glas izdaleka (Some hear his voice from far away). 
3. Nije još sve *čulo* (Not everything has been heard yet). 
4. *Čuješ* li njegovo zvono? (Do you hear his bell?).
5. *Čujući* to, svi su napustili prostoriju (Hearing that, everyone left the room).